Comedian Woli Arole has asked his fans if he can substitute air freshener with body spray. The comic, who in the video tied a blue towel around his chest, said he had misplaced his body spray and needed to head out. He also begged that netizens should not hurl abuses at him.   Burna wishes to make Portable’s picture album cover     I’m drained, DJ Cuppy cries out     How Mavin records can sign upcoming acts – Don Jazzy   He said: “Good morning guys, please I need your advice on something, please don’t abuse me. “I’m going out, I’m about to freshen up now. I can’t find my body spray. Please can I use air freshener? That’s just the question. Don’t abuse me. “Will I smell good? What’s your opinion? Cause it also sprays so can I use it? Thank you.”